         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Acadèmie international de Géographie botanique ¶ Dear Sir, —‚ ¶  ¶ I beg to inform you that you are elected by a decision of the Director of this Academy (15 July) a member  ¶ Associé libre ¶  of the ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">­</seg>93.07.21a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>To Henry Ridley</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RBG Kew, Letters to H. N. Ridley, vol. 4, f. 251.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">The MS is a pre-paid French Carte Postale, postmarked twice </seg>Le Mans Sarthe 8<seg style="">E </seg>| 21 Juil 93 <seg style="font-style: italic; ">and once</seg> Singapore Au 16 93,<seg style="font-style: italic; "> addressed to</seg>
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Mr Ridley | Director of the Botanic Garden | Singapore | Straits Settlements | Establissements Detroits. </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The note was not written by M but, presumably, by Hector Léveillé, and was probably written without M’s knowledge.</p>
               </note>Acadèmie international de Géographie botanique</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear Sir, —‚</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I beg to inform you that you are elected by a decision of the Director of this Academy (15 July) a member <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Associé libre</hi>
               </seg> of the same.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your nomination will be published in the number of Ist September of the Review "<seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Le Monde des Plantes</hi>
               </seg>" journal of the Society.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Le Monde des plantes</seg>, no. 24 (1 September 1893), p. 386.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Your[s] truly</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Baron Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Director</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">H. Léveillé</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Secretary</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">104 Rue de Flore. Le Mans. (Sarthe). France.</p>
